[30;1m1188 | [0m[35m    involved in this circuit have *next[i] = i*. We can see that if *next[i] = j*, where[0m
[30;1m1189 | [0m[35m    *i* and *j* are *different* values, then nodes *i* and *j* are both on the main circuit.[0m

[30;1m14 | [0m[35mlocal installation of CPLEX, not on Cplexcloud.[0m

[30;1m16 | [0m[35mAt each node, all progress listeners attached to the model receive progress data[0m
[30;1m17 | [0m[35mthrough a `notify_progress` method, with an instance of :class:`~ProgressData`.[0m
[30;1m18 | [0m[35mThis named tuple class contains information about solve time, objective value,[0m
[30;1m19 | [0m[35mbest bound, gap and nodes, but no variable values.[0m
